Package com.ryder.globalContainers

Class ActiveDataContainer

java.lang.Object
com.ryder.globalContainers.ActiveDataContainer
public class ActiveDataContainer extends Object
Global static container of plant protection products. Allows to easy access to every product in every fragment of code. Contains same data under ID key, codeName key and permission number key. Keys are based at given models.

    • getStats

      public static int[] getStats()
      List of stats based of collected data.
      Order of data:
      1. number of every product stored in
      2. every new product (that is not read from tabels_for_import.xlsx)
      3. number of products stored in bin
      4. number of products that doesn't contain dose info
      5. number of products that doesn't contain grace period info
      6. number of products that doesn't contain treatments info
      Returns:
      array with statistics of current models stored in
